prediction.sparql:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?dog ?dogLabel ( ( YEAR( ?death ) - YEAR( ?birth ) ) AS ?lifespan ) WHERE {
  ?dog wdt:P31 wd:Q144 .
  ?dog wdt:P569 ?birth .
  ?dog wdt:P570 ?death .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?dog rdfs:label ?dogLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?dogLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?lifespan )
LIMIT 1
OFFSET 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?discipline ?disciplineLabelGerman WHERE {
  ?discipline wdt:P279 * wd:Q11862829 .
  ?discipline rdfs:label ?disciplineLabelGerman .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?disciplineLabelGerman ) , "linguistik" ) ) FILTER ( LANG( ?disciplineLabelGerman ) = "de" )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?country ?countryLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q327818 wdt:P17 ?country .
  ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?countryLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?character ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?character wdt:P31 wd:Q95074 .
  ?character wdt:P106 wd:Q11397897 .
  ?character wdt:P21 wd:Q6581072 .
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?year1 ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 p:P166 ?statement1 .
  ?statement1 ps:P166 wd:Q674359 .
  ?statement1 pq:P585 ?date1 .
  BIND( YEAR( ?date1 ) AS ?year1 ) .
  wd:Q25369 p:P166 ?statement2 .
  ?statement2 ps:P166 wd:Q674359 .
  ?statement2 pq:P585 ?date2 .
  BIND( YEAR( ?date2 ) AS ?year2 ) .
  FILTER ( ?year1 = ?year2 )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 p:P54 ?statement1 .
  ?statement1 ps:P54 wd:Q121783 ; pq:P580 ?start1 ; pq:P582 ?end1 .
  wd:Q25369 p:P54 ?statement2 .
  ?statement2 ps:P54 wd:Q121783 ; pq:P580 ?start2 ; pq:P582 ?end2 .
  FILTER ( ?start1 <= "2000-12-31" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end1 >= "2000-01-01" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) .
  FILTER ( ?start2 <= "2000-12-31" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end2 >= "2000-01-01" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?place ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?place wdt:P361 wd:Q1144286 .
  ?place wdt:P31 ?type .
  ?type wdt:P279 * wd:Q515 .
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?genre ?genreLabel ( STRLEN( ?genreLabel ) AS ?length ) WHERE {
  wd:Q68061 wdt:P136 ?genre .
  ?genre rdfs:label ?genreLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?genreLabel ) = "en" )
}
ORDER BY ?length
LIMIT 1

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( ?statement ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  wd:Q110719 p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q18130478 .
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?event ?eventLabel ?cause ?causeLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q430 wdt:P31 wd:Q16521 .
  wd:Q55811 rdfs:label ?eventLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?eventLabel ) = "en" ) .
  wd:Q55811 wdt:P828 ?cause .
  ?cause rdfs:label ?causeLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?causeLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?femaleFormLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q39018 wdt:P3321 ?femaleFormLabelEntity .
  ?femaleFormLabelEntity rdfs:label ?femaleFormLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?femaleFormLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q641 p:P17 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P17 wd:Q131964 .
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( ( ?populationRecent - ?population2010 ) / ?population2010 * 100 AS ?growthRate ) WHERE {
  wd:Q183 p:P1082 ?popStatement2010 .
  ?popStatement2010 ps:P1082 ?population2010 .
  ?popStatement2010 pq:P585 ?date2010 .
  FILTER ( YEAR( ?date2010 ) = 2010 ) wd:Q183 p:P1082 ?popStatementRecent .
  ?popStatementRecent ps:P1082 ?populationRecent .
  ?popStatementRecent pq:P585 ?dateRecent .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?dateRecent )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?place WHERE {
  ?place wdt:P17 wd:Q39 ; wdt:P625 ?coord .
  BIND( geof:latitude ( ?coord ) AS ?lat ) FILTER ( ?lat > 47.8 )
}
LIMIT 1

prediction.sparql:
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?person WHERE {
  ?person p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q1048744 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?startDate .
  FILTER ( ?startDate < "1964-10-14T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?film ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?film wdt:P31 wd:Q11424 ; wdt:P136 wd:Q842256 ; wdt:P577 ?date .
  FILTER ( YEAR( ?date ) = 1978 ) .
  FILTER ( ?film != wd:Q267721 ) .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?marianaLowestPoint ?marianaDepth ?everestElevation WHERE {
  wd:Q510 wdt:P1589 ?marianaLowestPoint .
  ?marianaLowestPoint wdt:P2044 ?marianaDepth .
  wd:Q513 wdt:P2044 ?everestElevation .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( ?game ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?game wdt:P31 wd:Q7889 ; wdt:P577 ?releaseDate .
  FILTER ( YEAR( ?releaseDate ) = 2016 ) .
  FILTER ( ?game != wd:Q24514682 ) .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?occupation ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?winner wdt:P166 wd:Q37922 .
  ?winner wdt:P26 ?spouse .
  ?spouse wdt:P106 ?occupation .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?country ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q6256 .
  ?country wdt:P37 ?language .
  ?language wdt:P279 * wd:Q23526 .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

  ?winner wdt:P166 wd:Q123737 .
  ?winner wdt:P27 ?country .
}
GROUP BY ?country
ORDER BY DESC ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?winner ) )

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT ?stateBrooke ?stateColin WHERE {
  wd:Q2926117 wdt:P19 / wdt:P131 * ?stateBrooke .
  wd:Q87192979 wdt:P19 / wdt:P131 * ?stateColin .
  FILTER ( ?stateBrooke = ?stateColin )

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
